	* wordgen.c (options): Added `--prefix' and `--postfix' command line
	switchesa
	* configure.ac: Included license.

2008-05-25  Henri Häkkinen  <henux@users.sourceforge.net>

	* wordgen.c (options): added `--lowercase', `--uppercase', `--digits',
	`--xdigits', `--Xdigits', `--punctuations', `--alpha', `--alnum' and
	`--ascii' command line switches.

